@startuml 数据管理模块用例图

left to right direction

actor "教师" as Teacher
actor "学生" as Student
actor "学校管理员" as Admin
actor "系统" as System

usecase "数据采集" as UC1
usecase "数据查询" as UC2
usecase "数据可视化" as UC3
usecase "实时数据展示" as UC4
usecase "历史数据导出" as UC5

System --> UC1
Teacher --> UC2
Student --> UC2
Admin --> UC2
Teacher --> UC3
Student --> UC3
Admin --> UC3
Teacher --> UC4
Student --> UC4
Admin --> UC4
Teacher --> UC5
Admin --> UC5

UC2 .> UC3 : <<include>>
UC2 .> UC4 : <<include>>
UC5 .> UC2 : <<extend>>

note right of UC1
  系统自动接收设备上报的
  传感器数据并存储
end note

note right of UC3
  使用图表展示数据趋势
  支持折线图、柱状图等
end note

@enduml